message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.COMM, cs.AI, cs.SY - This paper discusses the development of wireless networks for smart systems of the future, which involves a combination of networking, information theory, communication, artificial intelligence, and system engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.COMM (Communication), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
